flowchart TD
    Start([Visit Sugbu Shop Hub]) --> Browse[Browse Shops & Products]

    Browse --> Product[Open a Product Page]
    Product --> LoggedIn{Logged In?}

    LoggedIn -- No --> Auth[Sign Up or Log In]
    Auth --> Product

    LoggedIn -- Yes --> Action{Choose Action}

    Action -- Ask a Question --> Chat[Chat with Seller]
    Chat --> Browse

    Action -- Want to Buy --> AddCart[Add to Cart]
    AddCart --> MoreShopping{Continue Shopping?}
    MoreShopping -- Yes --> Browse
    MoreShopping -- No --> Checkout

    Checkout[Go to Checkout] --> Address[Enter or Select Shipping Address]
    Address --> PlaceOrder[Place Order]
    PlaceOrder --> PayNow[Make Payment]
    PayNow --> Confirmed[Order Confirmed!]

    Confirmed --> Track[Track Order Status\nPending → Confirmed → Preparing → Shipped]
    Track --> Arrived{Package Arrived?}

    Arrived -- Yes --> ConfirmReceipt[Confirm Receipt]
    ConfirmReceipt --> Review[Leave a Product Review]
    Review --> Done([Happy Customer!])

    Arrived -- Not Yet / Issue --> Problem{What is the issue?}
    Problem -- Chat with Seller --> MsgSeller[Open Conversation with Seller]
    Problem -- Formal Complaint --> Ticket[Submit a Support Ticket]

    MsgSeller --> Resolved([Issue Resolved])
    Ticket --> AdminReview[Admin Reviews Ticket]
    AdminReview --> ForceResolve[Admin Overrides Order or Mediates]
    ForceResolve --> Resolved
